<#include "../commons/header.ftl" />
    <title>洗车</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="${_RESOURCES}/css/carWash/kcarWash.css?v=${_version}"/>
    <script src="${_RESOURCES}/js/carWash/kcarWash.js?v=${_version}" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
</head>
<body class="no-cache">
    <header class="header">
        <span class="back"></span>
        <h1>洗车</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="number">
            <div>
                <p>洗车次数</p>
                <p class="washNumber">0</p>
            </div>
            <div class="washCode">
                <p>我的洗车券</p>
                <p class="codeNumber">0</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carWash">
            <div class="serve">
                <a href="${_ROOT}/user/order.html?type=-1">我的订单</a>
                <a href="${_ROOT}/user/order.html?type=1">待服务</a>
                <a href="${_ROOT}/user/order.html?type=3">已完成</a>
            </div>
            <div class="serveFlow">
                <h2>服务流程</h2>
                <div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="instruction">
                <p>使用说明：用户点击立即洗车，我们会给您发送一张洗车券，用户把洗车券码给洗车网点商家，商家根据券码为用户提供服务，
                    服务完成会后券码失效。洗车券有使用时效，请勿重复兑换</p>
            </div>
            <div class="operate">
                <a id="toCarWash" href="javascript:void(0)" >立即洗车</a><!--href="${_ROOT}/carwash/kwashCode.html"-->
                <a href="http://zhida.kuanter.com/point.html">网点查询</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
